OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1776280294
OL,3,CWales start World Cup campaign with
OL,4,Cdecisive win over Albania
OL,6,FAway goals scored is what currently
OL,7,Fseparates the two sides.It took 15
OL,8,Fminutes for Cain to open the scoring,
OL,9,Flatching onto a perfectly-weighted
OL,10,Fpass from Mared Griffiths before
OL,11,Fsliding it beyond Rajmonda Spahiu in
OL,12,Fthe Albanian goal.
OL,14,FLeicester's Cain then turned provider
OL,15,Fafter the half hour mark when her
OL,16,Fcross into the middle was fumbled by
OL,17,FSpahiu, with Elise Hughes reacting
OL,18,Fquickest to thrash the ball into the
OL,19,Fnet from close range.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/4
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
