PN,46303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1776280294
OL,3,CWales start World Cup campaign with
OL,4,Cdecisive win over Albania
OL,6,FShortly after half time, Rhiannon
OL,7,FRoberts headed home from Griffiths'
OL,8,Fcross, ending the game as a contest.
OL,10,FBut Cain added her second just before
OL,11,Fthe hour mark. She met Lily Woodham's
OL,12,Fcross in the middle of the six-yard
OL,13,Fbox and poked it home.
OL,15,FWales surrendered top spot in the
OL,16,Fgroup owing to Czechia's 5-0 win in
OL,17,FMontenegro but the group is looking
OL,18,Flike it will be decided when the two
OL,19,Ftop sides meet in Cardiff in the final
OL,20,Fround.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/4
